陈巍与花滑的缘分始于2002年的盐湖城冬奥会，他的姐姐参加了开幕式节目《光之子》的演出。由于盐湖城建了许多冰场，冰上活动相当受欢迎。三岁的陈巍原希望追随哥哥打冰球，当守门员，但因年纪太小，便穿上姐姐的冰鞋先练花滑，从而展开花样滑冰生涯。

作为花滑的延伸训练，陈巍七岁起在{{Link-en|西部芭蕾学院|Ballet West}}<ref name=ballet/>接受六年正规芭蕾课程，每周六堂课，八岁能做芭蕾空转两圈，早早展露天分，他曾参加西部芭蕾舞团《[[天鹅湖|天鹅湖]]》、《[[睡美人|睡美人]]》、《[[胡桃夹子|胡桃夹子]]》等芭蕾舞剧演出。 <ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.dancemagazine.com/nathan-chen-ballet-2531928874.html |title = This Former Ballet Kid Is Heading To The Olympics—And Is Expected To Win |author = Jennifer Stahl |date = 2/6/18 |publisher = 美国舞蹈杂志 |accessdate = 2018-03-26 |archive-date = 2018-03-27 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180327023401/http://www.dancemagazine.com/nathan-chen-ballet-2531928874.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>参加区域及全国的高级体操赛事七年达九级。他还加入冰球队，师事世界级钢琴家，并赢得过犹他州古典钢琴比赛冠军。这些训练使他具备流畅的舞蹈表现能力，音乐敏锐度，体操控制身体的能力，冰球的强悍，紧凑的行程课表也培养出有效运用时间的纪律。<ref>{{Cite news | url=http://www.espn.com/espn/feature/story/_/id/22257148/figure-skater-nathan-chen-take-sport-new-heights-2018-winter-olympics | title=One Giant Leap | author=Bonnie D. Ford | date=2018-02-08 | publisher=ESPN | accessdate=2018-03-25 | archive-date=2018-03-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180329150721/http://www.espn.com/espn/feature/story/_/id/22257148/figure-skater-nathan-chen-take-sport-new-heights-2018-winter-olympics | dead-url=no }}</ref>

由于花滑训练花费昂贵，家境小康的陈巍仍曾陷买不起冰鞋，比赛付不起教练交通食宿费用的窘境。他学习花滑的历程仰赖许多人士协助，支付冰鞋和训练的费用，其中{{Link-en|迈克尔·韦斯|Michael Weiss (figure skater)}}基金会曾于十年内赞助陈巍奖学金约七万五千美元，<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/winter-olympics-2018/2018/02/02/nathan-chen-elevates-usa-hopes-olympic-skating-gold/1089579001/ |title = Nathan Chen elevates U.S. hopes for figure skating gold at Winter Olympics |author = Christine Brennan |date = 2/2/18 |publisher = USA TODAY SPORTS |accessdate = 2018-03-26 |archive-date = 2018-03-30 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180330051630/https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/winter-olympics-2018/2018/02/02/nathan-chen-elevates-usa-hopes-olympic-skating-gold/1089579001/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>他的教练也曾提供财务支援。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://rsport.ria.ru/interview/20171209/1129822500.html |title = Натан Чен: "Своей победой в Москве я расстроил кучу людей" |date = 10/12/18 |publisher = Россия сегодня |accessdate = 2018-03-28 |archive-date = 2018-03-28 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180328232741/https://rsport.ria.ru/interview/20171209/1129822500.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>

陈巍在奥运夺金后受访，每每感谢并强调母亲是幕后功臣，说她身兼数分差，是他见过最努力工作的人<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.worldjournal.com/wj/story/121471/6128978 | title = 冬奧男單花式滑冰金牌陳巍 與南加冰迷座談  | date = 27/2/22 | publisher =世界新聞網 }}</ref>。他提到小时候为了接受训练，母亲不辞路途遥远，开车载他来回于盐湖城和南加州之间，由于家境不够宽裕，必须凑錢支付教练，并睡在车里。教练知道他的状况后，只收他们能负担的钱，继续指导他。教练有时会试着把钱还给他，但陈巍总是试着把钱塞在教练的口袋里。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://edition.cnn.com/videos/sports/2022/02/11/nathan-chen-winter-olympics-post-game-wire-intv-ovn-intl-hnk-vpx.cnn | title = Nathan Chen reacts to winning his first Olympic gold  | date = 11/2/22 | publisher = CNN }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web | url = https://www.wsj.com/articles/nathan-chen-olympics-figure-skating-11644470997 | title = Nathan Chen’s Golden Hour  | date = 10/2/22 | publisher = 华尔街日报 }}</ref>

陈巍自小以来，比赛服装多由母亲制作，在美国队代表简介中，媽媽的名字多次出現為服装设计。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://usfigureskatingfanzone.com/roster.aspx?rp_id=44 |title = 2019-20 Figure Skating Roster |publisher = usfigureskatingfanzone.com |accessdate = 2019-12-12 |archive-date = 2019-10-20 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191020230726/https://usfigureskatingfanzone.com/roster.aspx?rp_id=44 |dead-url = no }}</ref> 2019-2020赛季自由滑《火箭人》服装被戏称为“巴士花椅套”，也出自母亲之手。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://usfigureskatingfanzone.com/news/2019/10/20/figure-skating-chen-hubbell-donohue-take-skate-america-titles.aspx |title = Chen, Hubbell and Donohue Take Skate America Titles |author = Darci Miller |date = 2019-10-20 |publisher = usfigureskatingfanzone.com |accessdate = 2019-11-03 |archive-date = 2019-10-24 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191024002525/https://usfigureskatingfanzone.com/news/2019/10/20/figure-skating-chen-hubbell-donohue-take-skate-america-titles.aspx |dead-url = no }}</ref>

曾经也是花滑女单选手的知名时尚设计师[[王薇薇|王薇薇]]自2018年奥运赛季起，担任他的服装设计。风格低调优雅的陈巍不喜亮片，或服装过度装饰，<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.nytimes.com/2018/02/15/sports/olympics/nathan-chen-figure-skating.html |title = Why Nathan Chen Shuns Sequins |author = Jeré Longman |date = 2/15/18 |publisher = 纽约时报 |accessdate = 2020-01-27 |archive-date = 2020-01-27 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200127053715/https://www.nytimes.com/2018/02/15/sports/olympics/nathan-chen-figure-skating.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>追求舒适的服装风格屡屡引发讨论，2020-2021赛季自由滑重复使用编舞家席琳·鮑爾恩的旧服装，也成为话题。[[王薇薇|王薇薇]]受访表示，陈巍深入参与整个设计过程，例如对香颂《波西米亚人》的服装，要求样子像西装，但穿起来感觉像耐克T恤。由于陈巍在冰上突破极限，所以服装设计也应如此，[[王薇薇|王薇薇]]为他的自由滑节目[[艾尔顿·约翰|艾尔顿·约翰]]《火箭人》采用过萤光黄色，也研究过太空探索和火箭发射设计银河印花，其中一款如冰上爆发的火焰，<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.nbcnewyork.com/news/sports/beijing-winter-olympics/its-a-great-privilege-vera-wang-discusses-designing-for-olympic-figure-skater-nathan-chen/3544166/ | title = ‘It's a Great Privilege': Vera Wang Discusses Designing for Olympic Figure Skater Nathan Chen  | date = 10/2/22 | publisher = NBC NEW YORK }}</ref>[[2022年冬季奧林匹克運動會|2022北京冬奥会]]的那一款则随陈巍在冰上滑行，产生乾坤旋转宇宙浩瀚的视觉效果。CNN时尚评论“有時少即是多（中略），長袖 T 恤上的圖案像星球爆发，震撼世界。”<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://edition.cnn.com/style/article/figure-skating-outfits-2022-olympics-spt-cec/index.html | title = These are some of the most memorable figure skating fashions from this year's Winter Olympics  | date = 19/2/22 | publisher = CNN style }}</ref>

陈巍曾在中学修过中文课，在家母亲也与他说中文。从小到大经常和他一起出征比赛的[[陈楷雯|陈楷雯]]曾受访指出，美国队的华裔单人选手或多或少都会一些普通话，但这方面，她有自信强过陈巍。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://cn.nytimes.com/sports/20220210/figure-skating-chen-asian-americans/ | title = 亚裔美国人撑起美国花样滑冰“半边天” | date = 10/2/22 | publisher = 纽约时报中文版 }}</ref>

== 花滑生涯 ==
=== 早年经历 ===
陈巍从三岁起就开始学习[[花样滑冰|花样滑冰]]，并在一年后（2003年）首度参加花滑赛事。从2007年到2009年，他获得了参加美国少年花样滑冰锦标赛少年组和中级组的资格。在2007年和2008年的全美花滑青少年锦标赛中，陈巍分别拿下了少年组第十名和第三名的成绩；而在2009年，他拿下了中级组的银牌。

在2009-10赛季里，陈巍晋级到新手组。在2010年于[[华盛顿州|华盛顿州]][[斯波坎縣|斯波坎縣]]举办的[[美國花式溜冰錦標賽|美国花样滑冰锦标赛]]上，陈巍拿下了新手组冠军，并以10岁的年纪成为美国花样滑冰锦标赛史上最年轻的新手组冠军。<ref name=rsp/> 由于陈巍的年纪偏小，使得他在2010-11赛季里依旧被划归在新手组，从而他蝉联了2011年于[[北卡罗来纳州|北卡罗来纳州]][[格林斯伯勒_(北卡罗来纳州)|格林斯伯勒]]举办的美国花样滑冰锦标赛新手组冠军。<ref name=IN110124/><ref name=GS110124/>

在2011-12赛季里，陈巍在全国级别赛事中晋升到少年组级别。此时他师从{{Link-en|耶夫根·车尔尼索娃|Evgenia Chernyshova}}，并前往[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]]的{{Link-en|箭头湖 (加利福尼亚州)|Lake Arrowhead, California|箭头湖}}与跳跃专家{{Link-en|拉斐尔·阿鲁秋尼杨|Rafael Arutyunyan}}合作。<ref name=IFS110703/> 2011年12月中旬，拉斐尔·阿鲁秋尼杨成为了陈巍的主教练。<ref name=IN120123/> 陈巍在2012年1月24日于加利福尼亚州[[圣何塞_(美国加州)|圣何塞]]举行的美国花样滑冰锦标赛上摘下少年组冠军。<ref name=GS120125/> 作为陈巍的第一次国际亮相，他摘取了2012年在[[意大利|意大利]][[塞尔瓦迪瓦尔加尔德纳|塞尔瓦迪瓦尔加尔德纳]]举办的{{Link-en|加迪纳杯春季赛|Gardena Spring Trophy}}的新手组冠军。<ref name=IN120411/><ref name=IN120414/>

=== 2012-2013赛季 ===
在2012-13赛季里，陈巍依旧在全国范围内保持着少年组的参赛水平。并且他在这个赛季达到了[[国际滑冰联盟青少年花样滑冰大奖赛|国际滑冰联盟青少年花样滑冰大奖赛]]（JGP）系列赛的参赛门槛年龄（13周岁）。<ref name=GS120125/> 陈巍的第一个JGP系列赛便是2012年9月12日到16日在[[奥地利|奥地利]][[林茨|林茨]]举办的{{Link-en|国际滑冰联盟青少年花样滑冰大奖赛奥地利站|ISU Junior Grand Prix in Austria|奥地利国际青少年大奖赛}}。<ref name=USFSA-1314comp/> 他以迄今JGP赛事最高分（222.00分）获得了金牌。<ref name=IN120915/> 2012年10月初，由于陈巍在{{Link-en|国际滑冰联盟青少年滑冰大奖赛克罗地亚站|ISU Junior Grand Prix in Croatia|克罗地亚青少年大奖赛}}[[短节目|短节目]]中小腿受伤而退赛，进而导致他无缘本赛季[[国际滑冰联盟青少年花样滑冰大奖赛|国际滑冰联盟青少年花样滑冰大奖赛总决赛]]。<ref name=IN121006/> 2013年1月22日，陈巍在[[内布拉斯加州|内布拉斯加州]][[奥马哈_(内布拉斯加州)|奥马哈]]举行的美国花样滑冰锦标赛上，拿下少年组铜牌。<ref name=IN130123/>

=== 2013-2014赛季 ===
陈巍赢得国际滑冰联盟青少年花样滑冰大奖赛墨西哥站和白俄罗斯站金牌，进入日本福冈举办的总决赛，获得铜牌。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.isuresults.com/results/gpf1314/CAT005RS.HTM |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2017-12-03 |archive-date=2015-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150516141307/http://www.isuresults.com/results/gpf1314/CAT005RS.HTM |dead-url=no }}</ref>1月9日他以213.76分创下美国青少年男子纪录，第二度获得美国锦标赛青少年组冠军。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://web.icenetwork.com/news/2014/01/09/66435988/little-chen-choo-choos-way-to-junior-mens-romp |title = Little Chen Choo Choos way to junior men's romp |author = Amy Rosewater |date = 1/9/14 |publisher = icenetwork |access-date = 2017-12-24 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171030171014/http://web.icenetwork.com/news/2014/01/09/66435988/little-chen-choo-choos-way-to-junior-mens-romp |archive-date = 2017-10-30 |dead-url = yes }}</ref>2014年3月于保加利亚举办的青少年世锦赛中赢得铜牌。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.isuresults.com/results/wjc2014/CAT001RS.HTM |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2017-12-03 |archive-date=2017-03-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170318211437/http://www.isuresults.com/results/wjc2014/CAT001RS.HTM |dead-url=no }}</ref>

=== 2014－2015赛季 ===
[[File:Nathan_Chen_2015.png|thumb]]

在2014-2015赛季中，陈巍开始挑战国内的青年组赛事。在2014年11月举行的太平洋地区锦标赛上，他在[[自由滑|自由滑]]中完成了一次毫无瑕疵的后外点冰四周跳接后外点冰两周跳（4T+2T），<ref name=PS2015/> 赢得了该项赛事的冠军，并成功晋级在[[北卡罗来纳州|北卡罗来纳州]][[格林斯博罗_(北卡罗来纳州)|格林斯博罗]]举办的2015年[[美國花式溜冰錦標賽|美国花样滑冰锦标赛]]。

=== 2015-2016赛季 ===
2015–16国际滑冰联盟青少年花样滑冰大奖系列赛事中，陈巍首度于国际大赛中完成四周跳，斩获大奖赛美国站和西班牙站两项金牌，2015年12月于巴塞隆纳总决赛获得冠军。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://goldenskate.com/2015/12/nathan-chen-2/ |title = Nathan Chen readies for 2016 U.S. Nationals |author = Paula Slater |date = 2015-12-13 |publisher = Golden Skate |accessdate = 2017-12-03 |archive-date = 2017-12-04 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171204171054/https://goldenskate.com/2015/12/nathan-chen-2/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>
2016年1月，陈巍于美国锦标赛成为史上第一位在短节目完成两个四周跳，长节目完成四个四周跳的美国选手，<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.teamusa.org/News/2016/January/23/Nathan-Chen-Makes-History-As-First-To-Land-Two-Quads-In-Short-Program-At-US-Championships |title = Nathan Chen Makes History As First To Land Two Quads In Short Program At U.S. Championships |author = CHRÖS MCDOUGALL |date = 2016-01-23 |publisher = United States Olympic Committee |accessdate = 2017-12-03 |archive-date = 2019-11-29 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191129003345/https://www.teamusa.org/News/2016/January/23/Nathan-Chen-Makes-History-As-First-To-Land-Two-Quads-In-Short-Program-At-US-Championships |dead-url = no }}</ref>获得铜牌，却在随后表演项目的跳跃动作中伤及左髋，于1月27日进行手术治疗，因而错过其后的世界锦标赛等赛事。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://usfigureskating.org/story?id=88959&type=media |title = CHEN UNDERGOES LEFT HIP SURGERY |date = 1/28/16 |publisher = U.S. Figure Skating |access-date = 2017-02-27 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181217111620/https://usfigureskating.org/story?id=88959&type=media |archive-date = 2018-12-17 |dead-url = yes }}</ref>
陈巍在加州的美国奥运训练中心进行为期一个月的复健，到了五月赴科罗拉多斯普林斯的美国奥运训练中心进行非冰上训练，于七月恢复完整冰上训练。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://web.icenetwork.com/news/2016/08/26/197645372 |title = Chen hopes to put injury bug behind him in 2016-17 |author = Lynn Rutherford |date = 8/26/16 |publisher = icenetwork |accessdate = 2017-02-27 |archive-date = 2017-01-17 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170117020855/http://web.icenetwork.com/news/2016/08/26/197645372 |dead-url = no }}</ref>

=== 2016-2017赛季 ===
迎接第一个国际成人组赛季，赴密西根坎顿市委托[[玛丽娜·祖耶娃|玛丽娜·祖耶娃]]编舞，为提升节目内容分PCS，留训接受[[玛丽娜·祖耶娃|玛丽娜·祖耶娃]]和Oleg Epstein指导。为准备第一个成人组国际赛季，他在髋骨受伤六个月后，开始练习勾手四周跳（4Lz）和后内点冰四周跳（4F）。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://web.icenetwork.com/news/2016/10/29/207519314/ |title = Chan, Chen in Canton with different goals in mind |author = Lynn Rutherford |date = 10/29/16 |publisher = icenetwork |accessdate = 2017-02-27 |archive-date = 2017-02-11 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170211080112/http://web.icenetwork.com/news/2016/10/29/207519314/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>

[[File:2016–2017_Grand_Prix_of_Figure_Skating_Final_Nathan_Chen_IMG_4000_03.jpg|thumb]]]]
具备四种四周跳－后外点冰跳（4T），后内跳（4S），后内点冰跳（4F），勾手跳（4Lz）－陈巍于2016年芬兰杯取得本赛季首面金牌。其后的大奖赛事中，陈巍在2016年法国站的短节目和长节目，都成功完成组合跳跃勾手四周跳接外点冰三周跳（4Lz+3T），以及后内点冰四周跳。大奖赛法国站取得第四名成绩后，陈巍回归加州{{Link-en|拉斐尔·阿鲁秋尼杨|Rafael Arutyunyan}}的训练团队。

获2016年NHK杯银牌后，首度晋级成人组大奖赛总决赛。在法国马赛举办的总决赛中，他于长节目完成四个四周跳，最终取得银牌，是继[[叶甫根尼·普鲁申科|普鲁申科]]（1999年16岁之龄）之后，于大奖赛总决赛得奖的最年轻的选手（17岁）。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://web.icenetwork.com/news/2017/01/18/213823372/ |title = Chen revamps programs in preparation for KC |author = Lynn Rutherford |date = 1/18/17 |publisher = icenetwork |accessdate = 2017-02-27 |archive-date = 2017-01-31 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170131200943/http://web.icenetwork.com/news/2017/01/18/213823372/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>

2017年美国锦标赛中，陈巍在短节目完成两个四周跳（4Lz+3T，4F），长节目完成五个四周跳（4Lz+3T，4F，4T+2T+2Lo，4T，4S），以美国滑冰史上最高成绩（短节目106.39，长节目 212.08分，总分318.47）及最高分差（55.44）赢得金牌。

二月赢得四大洲锦标赛金牌，成为国际滑冰联盟史上第三位短节目超过100分的选手，并取得国际赛事上总分超过300分的佳绩。

四月世界锦标赛于赫尔辛基举办，他虽然总共挑战了八个四周跳（短节目两个，长节目六个），由于冰鞋耗损导致失误，最终获得第六名，仍与获第七名的队友杰森·布朗，联手为美国取得三个奥运参赛名额。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.usfigureskating.org/story?id=90301&type=media |title = U.S. FIGURE SKATING ANNOUNCES WORLD, FOUR CONTINENTS AND WORLD JUNIOR TEAMS |date = 1/22/17 |publisher = U.S. Figure Skating |accessdate = 2017-02-27 |archive-date = 2017-01-22 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170122171206/http://www.usfigureskating.org/story?id=90301&type=media |dead-url = no }}</ref>陈巍的第一个成人组赛季，年度世界排名第三。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.isuresults.com/ws/wr2016-17/wrmen.htm |title = 2016-2017 ISU Season's World Ranking |publisher = 国际滑冰联盟 |accessdate = 2019-04-01 |archive-date = 2017-04-09 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170409065638/http://www.isuresults.com/ws/wr2016-17/wrmen.htm |dead-url = no }}</ref>

=== 2017－2018赛季（奥运赛季）===
[[File:Photos_–_World_Championships_2018_–_Men_(Medalists)_(10).jpg|thumb]]
九月于美国秋季國際經典賽拿下本赛季第一面金牌，发表知名编舞师{{Link-en|席琳·鮑爾恩|Shae-Lynn Bourne}}的短节目〈报应〉，及[[洛丽·尼科尔|洛丽·尼科尔]]的长节目〈末代舞者〉。他在长节目中完成后外四周跳（4L），成为首位在比赛中完成五种四周跳的选手（4T，4S，4Lo，4F，4Lz）。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://web.icenetwork.com/news/2017/09/15/254564678 |title = Chen powers way to gold in return to Salt Lake City |author = Philip Hersh |date = 9/16/17 |publisher = icenetwork |accessdate = 2017-12-03 |archive-date = 2017-09-16 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170916140748/http://web.icenetwork.com/news/2017/09/15/254564678 |dead-url = no }}</ref>

十月于大奖赛俄罗斯站，获得生涯第一个大奖赛金牌。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.isuresults.com/results/season1718/gprus2017/CAT001RS.HTM |title = ISU GP Rostelecom Cup 2017 - Men |date = 2017-11-25 |publisher = www.isuresults.com |accessdate = 2017-12-03 |archive-date = 2017-12-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171202033114/http://www.isuresults.com/results/season1718/gprus2017/CAT001RS.HTM |dead-url = no }}</ref>接着于美国站连获第二个金牌。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.isuresults.com/results/season1718/gpusa2017/CAT001RS.HTM |title = ISU GP 2017 Skate America - Men |date = 2017-11-25 |publisher = International Skating Union |accessdate = 2017-12-03 |archive-date = 2017-11-26 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171126223813/http://www.isuresults.com/results/season1718/gpusa2017/CAT001RS.HTM |dead-url = no }}</ref>他是本赛季唯一以不败纪录，最高积分晋级大奖总决赛男单选手。十二月在名古屋，获[[2017–18国际滑冰联盟花样滑冰大奖赛总决赛|大奖赛总决赛]]冠军。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.isuresults.com/results/season1718/gpf1718/data0190.htm |title = ISU Grand Prix Final 2017 - Men Result |date = 08/12/17 |publisher = 国际滑冰联盟 |accessdate = 2017-12-08 |archive-date = 2018-11-01 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181101204139/http://www.isuresults.com/results/season1718/gpf1718/data0190.htm |dead-url = no }}</ref>

曾是花滑选手的知名服装设计师[[王薇薇|王薇薇]]为陈巍设计比赛服装。在加州圣荷西举办的2018美国锦标赛中，陈巍成功完成七个四周跳（短节目两个，自由滑五个），以领先40分以上的优势卫冕全美冠军。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://web.icenetwork.com/news/2018/01/07/264376290/quad-mastery-sends-chen-to-top-of-us-podium |title = Quad mastery sends Chen to top of U.S. podium |author = Philip Hersh |date = 1/7/18 |publisher = ICENETWORK |accessdate = 2018-01-10 |archive-date = 2018-01-08 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180108162509/http://web.icenetwork.com/news/2018/01/07/264376290/quad-mastery-sends-chen-to-top-of-us-podium |dead-url = no }}</ref>

本赛季全战全胜的陈巍被视为[[2018年冬季奥林匹克运动会|平昌冬奥]]夺金的热门人选，挟带可口可乐，普利司通，联合航空，耐克，家乐氏等大厂商赞助的光环，背负着国家期望，却因压力过大导致奥运失利。首先举办的团体赛中，陈巍虽于男子短节目项目表现失常，美国队仍获得铜牌。然而男单赛事短节目的跳跃再度出现严重失误，排名落后至第17。失无所失的陈巍在长节目大胆挑战六次四周跳，以长节目排名第一的215.08高分（领先第二的金牌得主近9分），逆势上升至第5名。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://news.sina.com.tw/article/20180217/25858758.html |title = 從5種4周跳到6個4周跳 細數陳巍創造的花滑紀錄 |date = 17/2/18 |publisher = 北京新浪網 |access-date = 2018-05-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180502211613/http://news.sina.com.tw/article/20180217/25858758.html |archive-date = 2018-05-02 |dead-url = yes }}</ref>陈巍首次参赛奥运虽错失个人项目奖牌，却在本届奥运缔造划时代意义的长节目表演，创下最高技术分127.64分的历史记录，单一节目六次四周跳的创举坐实“四周跳之王”的头衔。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.washingtonpost.com/sports/olympics/nathan-chen-becomes-first-skater-in-history-to-hit-six-quads-in-competition/2018/02/16/613a1b66-1309-11e8-9570-29c9830535e5_story.html?utm_term=.07a118157faa |title = Nathan Chen reigns as ‘Quad King,’ but Yuzuru Hanyu takes skating’s crown |author = Liz Clarke |date = 2/16/18 |publisher = 华盛顿邮报 |accessdate = 2018-02-18 |archive-date = 2018-02-19 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180219043354/https://www.washingtonpost.com/sports/olympics/nathan-chen-becomes-first-skater-in-history-to-hit-six-quads-in-competition/2018/02/16/613a1b66-1309-11e8-9570-29c9830535e5_story.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>

一个月后，在米兰举办的世锦赛中，陈巍记取经验挥别奥运梦魇，短节目正常发挥占得领先。长节目原本預定五個四周跳，然而在其他選手相继严重失误后，他未選擇降低難度的保守策略，反而提高難度，完成六次四周跳，加上步法旋转全获最高定级4，创下长节目219.46分（历代第二），总分321.40（历代第二）<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.jsports.co.jp/press/article/N2018040209323206.html |title = ISU世界フィギュアスケート選手権 男子 レビュー |author = ウェイ・ション |date = 4/3/18 |publisher = J Sports |accessdate = 2018-04-04 |archive-date = 2018-04-04 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180404134700/https://www.jsports.co.jp/press/article/N2018040209323206.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>。陈巍以总分领先47.63分的史上最高分差，获得压倒性胜利，是2009年以来美国男子首度夺得世界冠军，<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_2042626 |title = 华裔少年夺美国花滑男单9年来首冠，他要感谢自己的中国家庭 |author = 蒲垚磊 |date = 3/26/18 |publisher = 澎湃新闻 |accessdate = 2018-03-28 |archive-date = 2018-03-28 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180328231454/http://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_2042626 |dead-url = no }}</ref>也是继2001年[[叶甫根尼·普鲁申科|普鲁申科]]夺金（时年18岁4个月）之后最年轻的世界冠军（18岁10个月）。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.isu.org/inside-single-pair-skating-ice-dance/figure-skating-other/news-fs/12060-nathan-chen-gives-usa-first-men-s-figure-skating-gold-in-nine-years?templateParam=15 |title = Nathan Chen gives USA first Men’s figure skating gold in nine years |date = 3/24/18 |publisher = 国际滑冰联盟 |accessdate = 2018-03-25 |archive-date = 2018-03-26 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180326065913/https://www.isu.org/inside-single-pair-skating-ice-dance/figure-skating-other/news-fs/12060-nathan-chen-gives-usa-first-men-s-figure-skating-gold-in-nine-years?templateParam=15 |dead-url = no }}</ref>除奥运外，本赛季全战全胜，年度世界排名第一。<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.isuresults.com/ws/wr2017-18/wrmen.htm|title = 2017-2018 ISU Season's World Ranking|date = 3/24/18|publisher = 国际滑冰联盟|accessdate = 2018-03-26|archive-date = 2018-03-30|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180330184233/http://www.isuresults.com/ws/wr2017-18/wrmen.htm|dead-url = no}}</ref>

=== 2018－2019赛季 ===
[[File:Winners-2018_GP_France-IMG_8447.jpg|thumb]]
[[File:Nathan_Chen_at_the_2018-19_Grand_Prix_Final.jpg|thumb]]
2018年秋进耶鲁大学，陈巍面临如何在学业与滑冰之间进行权衡。入住校舍的他，独自在学校曲棍球队冰场及校外一所冰场训练，并通过视频与远距离的教练解决技术上的问题。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.weibo.com/ttarticle/p/show?id=2309404353389642299226 |title = 从折戟平昌到圆梦埼玉 陈巍的这一年 |author = 闫海莹 |date = 2019-03-24 |publisher = 央视体育 |accessdate = 2019-04-01 |archive-date = 2019-04-01 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190401062120/https://www.weibo.com/ttarticle/p/show%3Fid%3D2309404353389642299226 |dead-url = no }}</ref>

大一新生陈巍趁着秋假参加大奖赛美国站，以总分280.57分，分差41.06分的优势取得胜利。这是大奖赛美国站自现行评分制度实施16年来，所有项目的最大分差。<ref>{{Cite news | url=https://olympics.nbcsports.com/2018/10/20/nathan-chen-wins-skate-america/ | title=Nathan Chen wins Skate America by largest margin in history | author=Nick Zaccardi | date=2018-10-20 | publisher=NBCSC | accessdate=2018-10-22 | archive-date=2018-10-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181022113324/https://olympics.nbcsports.com/2018/10/20/nathan-chen-wins-skate-america/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>自由滑189.99分以及总分，为平昌奥运后新规则实施以来，当时的的最高纪录。<ref>{{Cite news | url=https://www.olympicchannel.com/en/stories/news/detail/nathan-chen-retains-skate-america/?utm_source=Twitter&utm_medium=tw-post&utm_campaign=social-owned&utm_content=OCContent_OC%20Content&sf200471203=1 | title=NATHAN CHEN RETAINS SKATE AMERICA TITLE IN STYLE | date=2018-10-21 | publisher=Olympic Channel | accessdate=2018-10-22 | archive-date=2018-10-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181022113434/https://www.olympicchannel.com/en/stories/news/detail/nathan-chen-retains-skate-america/?utm_source=Twitter&utm_medium=tw-post&utm_campaign=social-owned&utm_content=OCContent_OC%20Content&sf200471203=1 | dead-url=no }}</ref>接连赢得大奖赛法国站冠军，为近十年来首位在大奖赛取得五连胜的男单选手，本赛季双胜的成绩获得总决赛参赛资格。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://olympics.nbcsports.com/2018/11/24/nathan-chen-wins-grand-prix-france/ |title=Nathan Chen rallies, wins GP France, sets possible Yuzuru Hanyu matchup |author=Nick Zaccardi |date=2018-11-24 |publisher=NBC Sports |accessdate=2018-11-29 |archive-date=2018-11-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181125080527/https://olympics.nbcsports.com/2018/11/24/nathan-chen-wins-grand-prix-france/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>12月于加拿大温哥华举办的大奖总决赛蝉联冠军，为1995年大奖总决赛举办以来，继[[叶甫根尼·普鲁申科|普鲁申科]]，[[陈伟群|陈伟群]]，[[羽生结弦|羽生结弦]]之后，第四位连霸的男单选手。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.teamusa.org/News/2018/December/08/Nathan-Chen-Repeats-As-Grand-Prix-Final-Champion-Keeping-Perfect-Season-Alive |title=Yale Freshman Nathan Chen Repeats As Grand Prix Final Champion, Keeping Perfect Season Alive |author=Nick Zaccardi |date=2018-12-08 |publisher=美国滑冰联盟 |accessdate=2018-12-11 |archive-date=2018-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181209123646/https://www.teamusa.org/News/2018/December/08/Nathan-Chen-Repeats-As-Grand-Prix-Final-Champion-Keeping-Perfect-Season-Alive |dead-url=no }}</ref>也是继[[塔拉·利平斯基|塔拉·利平斯基]]之后第二位在大奖总决赛连胜的美国单人花滑运动员。陈巍此赛自由滑技术分101.79改写本赛季新规则施行后新纪录。

这一年美国锦标赛在底特律举行，配置两个四周跳的短节目113.42分，四个四周跳的自由滑228.80分，总分342.22为花滑史上最高分數，雖不列為国际花滑联盟正式紀錄，零失误的惊天表现，为他连续赢得第三个美国冠军头衔，以绝对强势再度问鼎世锦赛王座。<ref>{{Cite news | url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/columnist/brennan/2019/01/27/us-mens-national-figure-skating-nathan-chen-third-title/2697110002/ | title=Nathan Chen balances Yale studies with third U.S. figure skating championship | author=Christine Brennan | date=2019-01-27 | publisher=USA TODAY | accessdate=2019-04-01 | archive-date=2019-04-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190401062116/https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/columnist/brennan/2019/01/27/us-mens-national-figure-skating-nathan-chen-third-title/2697110002/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>

陈巍利用学校春假出征于日本埼玉举行的世锦赛，他与日本名将[[羽生结弦|羽生结弦]]的对决堪称经典。这是自平昌冬奥会之后，两人在世界顶级赛场的首次交锋，陈巍继美锦赛后再度上演两套零失误的节目。滴水不漏的短节目107.40分，以领先近13分的优势位列第一。自由滑比赛中，在两届冬奥会冠军[[羽生结弦|羽生结弦]]完美发挥、自由滑和总成绩打破世界纪录的情况下，陈巍展示强大心理素质和超强实力，行云流水般完美的表演，滑出令人叹为观止的216.02分，总分323.42，一举打破羽生刚创造的自由滑和总成绩世界纪录，毫无悬念地成功卫冕。<ref>{{Cite news | url=http://newsxmwb.xinmin.cn/wentihui/wtrw/2019/03/24/31505902.html | title=芭蕾范儿 花滑腕儿 华裔小将陈巍蝉联花滑世锦赛冠军 | author=厉苒苒 | date=2019-01-27 | publisher=新民晚报 | accessdate=2019-04-01 | archive-date=2019-04-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190401062118/http://newsxmwb.xinmin.cn/wentihui/wtrw/2019/03/24/31505902.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>成为继亚古丁之后，在十多岁之龄卫冕的世界冠军，为21世纪以来第一人。也是继[[斯科特·汉密尔顿|斯科特·汉密尔顿]]之后，第一个卫冕世界冠军的美国男单选手。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://olympics.nbcsports.com/2019/03/25/by-any-measure-nathan-chens-performance-at-worlds-matches-standard-for-transcendent-greatness/ |title=By any measure, Nathan Chen’s performance at Worlds matches standard for transcendent greatness |author=Philip Hersh |date=2019-03-25 |publisher=NBC SPORTS |accessdate=2019-04-01 |archive-date=2019-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190330072713/https://olympics.nbcsports.com/2019/03/25/by-any-measure-nathan-chens-performance-at-worlds-matches-standard-for-transcendent-greatness/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>这场陈巍与[[羽生结弦|羽生结弦]]的经典之战，双双突破了110分技术分与300分总分，为双雄竞争的局面立下里程碑。<ref>{{Cite news| url=https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2019/mar/29/nathan-chen-yuzuru-hanyu-figure-skating| title=Nathan Chen v Yuzuru Hanyu: the rivalry that has taken over figure skating| author=Nick McCarvel| date=2019-03-29| publisher=英国卫报| accessdate=2019-04-01| archive-date=2021-02-20| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210220102827/https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2019/mar/29/nathan-chen-yuzuru-hanyu-figure-skating| dead-url=no}}</ref>陈巍近两个赛季12战11胜的傲人战绩，让他蝉联年度世界排名第一，世界总排名（三年合计）第一。<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.isuresults.com/ws/wr2018-19/wrmen.htm|title = 2018-2019 ISU Season's World Ranking|date = 3/24/18|publisher = 国际滑冰联盟|accessdate = 2019-04-01|archive-date = 2019-06-10|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190610172108/http://www.isuresults.com/ws/wr2018-19/wrmen.htm|dead-url = no}}</ref>

四月代表美国参加世界团体锦标赛，个人成绩排名第一，团体成绩第一。

